SkiFree cartridge — attribution
================================

This crate is a Rust homage to:

    Chris Pirih, "SkiFree" (1991)
    Originally distributed in Microsoft Entertainment Pack 3 for Windows.

Sprite assets in `assets/`:

    - sprite-characters.png
    - skifree-objects.png

are sourced from the open-source JavaScript port:

